OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,FSky and ITV are closing in on a deal
OL,7,Fthat would pave the way for the TV and
OL,8,Ftelecoms operator to take over the
OL,9,FUK's most-watched free-to-air
OL,10,Fcommercial broadcaster, with sources
OL,11,Fsuggesting that an agreement could be
OL,12,Freached within weeks.
OL,14,FThe proposal would see ITV split in
OL,15,Ftwo, with the television channels and
OL,16,Fits ITVX streaming service sold to
OL,17,FSky, while ITV shareholders retain
OL,18,Fownership of the studios business,
OL,19,Fwhich makes programmes for ITV and
OL,20,Fother media outlets, including the big
OL,21,FUS streamers like Disney.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,FI have spoken to multiple sources
OL,7,Ffamiliar with the negotiations, on
OL,8,Fboth sides of the transaction, who
OL,9,Fsaid there is growing confidence that
OL,10,Fkey elements of the deal are falling
OL,11,Finto place and that both Sky and ITV
OL,12,Fare keen to agree terms - although
OL,13,Fthey cautioned that no agreement has
OL,14,Fyet been finalised and discussions
OL,15,Fremain ongoing.
OL,17,F"It's gone on much longer than we had
OL,18,Fever thought likely, but there's no
OL,19,Fproblem," one source told me. "Within
OL,20,Fa month would be my guess."
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@IO]{D@_OU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,FThe proposed sale was first announced
OL,7,Fin November last year, but six months
OL,8,Fon, a detailed set of heads of terms
OL,9,Fhas yet to be signed.
OL,11,FIn ITV's trading update on Thursday
OL,12,Fmorning, shareholders were told the
OL,13,Fcompany remains in "active
OL,14,Fdiscussions" with Sky, but no
OL,15,Fexplanation was given for why the
OL,16,Fprocess is taking so long.
OL,26,@uD@TOUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,F"This is not a straightforward
OL,7,Ftakeover," another source said. "What
OL,8,Fwe are trying to do is separate a
OL,9,Fbusiness that has been intertwined for
OL,10,F70 years."
OL,12,FIn addition to a Share Purchase
OL,13,FAgreement - setting out what Sky is
OL,14,Fbuying, for how much and on what terms
OL,15,F- both sides must negotiate a Content
OL,16,FSupply Agreement covering programmes
OL,17,Fsuch as Love Island, I'm a Celebrity!
OL,18,Fand The Voice, which ITV Studios would
OL,19,Fcontinue to produce for the ITV
OL,20,Fchannel, along with Coronation Street
OL,21,Fand Emmerdale.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@JO]oD@aOUrD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,FThe final agreement will also cover
OL,7,Fthe sections of Sky's production
OL,8,Fbusiness set to move to ITV Studios as
OL,9,Fpart of the transaction - Sky owns
OL,10,FLove Productions, which makes The
OL,11,FGreat British Bake Off for Channel 4 -
OL,12,Fas well as the terms under which ITV's
OL,13,Fbrand and archive will be used.
OL,15,FNotionally, the deal is between Sky
OL,16,Fand ITV, but Comcast, the US media
OL,17,Fgroup that owns Sky, will have the
OL,18,Ffinal say. The contracts are currently
OL,19,Fbeing scrutinised by its legal team in
OL,20,Fthe United States.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,F"Decisions are being taken at Comcast
OL,7,FHQ level," a source told me. "(The
OL,8,Fdeal) is with a lot of lawyers."
OL,10,FIn one sense, this deal looks like a
OL,11,Frounding error for Comcast.
OL,13,FThe company is a US giant in the
OL,14,Ftruest sense, with annual group sales
OL,15,Fof more than #90 billion last year,
OL,16,Ffrom broadband, cable television,
OL,17,Fmobile telephony, Universal Studios
OL,18,Fand its theme parks.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@JO]oD@^OUoD@_pmpD@EpnpD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,FITV's Media & Entertainment division,
OL,7,Fwhich is being purchased, generated
OL,8,Fjust under #2 billion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,FYou can understand Comcast's caution.
OL,7,FIt is widely seen as having
OL,8,Fsignificantly overpaid when it bought
OL,9,FSky in 2018 - around a quarter of the
OL,10,F#31 billion purchase price has since
OL,11,Fbeen written off. As things stand, the
OL,12,Fpurchase price of #1.6 billion for
OL,13,FITV's broadcast business is unchanged,
OL,14,Falthough my understanding is that up
OL,15,Fto #200 million of that sum will be
OL,16,Fmade contingent on ITV's advertising
OL,17,Fincome holding up over the next few
OL,18,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,FThere's no guarantee it will. Live
OL,7,Fsport and big-budget drama are where
OL,8,Fthe viewers - and therefore the
OL,9,Fadvertising money - are. This summer's
OL,10,FWorld Cup is likely to boost ITV's
OL,11,Fperformance in the short term, but the
OL,12,Flonger-term trend is cause for concern.
OL,14,FSince the pandemic, when there was a
OL,15,Fsurge in households signing up to
OL,16,FNetflix, Apple TV and other US
OL,17,Fstreamers, the decline in traditional
OL,18,Ftelevision audiences has accelerated
OL,19,Ffor all the UK's public service
OL,20,Fbroadcasters - the BBC, Channel 4 and
OL,21,FChannel 5, as well as ITV.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,F"ITV isn't going to fall off a cliff
OL,7,Ftomorrow, but look at the market - the
OL,8,Fcompany is just about holding on to
OL,9,Fadvertising, and the direction of
OL,10,Ftravel is clear," a former Ofcom
OL,11,Fexecutive said.
OL,13,FSky, too, is struggling to hold off
OL,14,Fthe US streamers. Its advertising
OL,15,Frevenue has fallen; so too has the
OL,16,Fnumber of its television subscribers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,FSky has millions of mobile and
OL,7,Fbroadband customers in the UK, but the
OL,8,Fsubscription television business -
OL,9,Fincreasingly delivered over the
OL,10,Finternet rather than satellite - is
OL,11,Funder pressure.
OL,13,FNowadays, Sky's adverts positions
OL,14,Fitself as a service through which to
OL,15,Faccess Netflix, Disney and HBO apps as
OL,16,Fmuch as a place to watch its own
OL,17,Fcontent.
OL,19,FDominance in sport is Sky's big
OL,20,Fcommercial advantage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,FThe company recently struck a deal for
OL,7,Fthe rights to broadcast Formula 1 in
OL,8,Fthe UK until 2034.
OL,10,FPremier League football is the jewel
OL,11,Fin the crown. Over the years, Sky has
OL,12,Frepeatedly won the battle of the
OL,13,Fchequebooks - fighting off challenges
OL,14,Ffrom BT and others.
OL,16,FBut the streamers have even deeper
OL,17,Fpockets and are developing a taste for
OL,18,Fsport. The next auction process begins
OL,19,Fnext year. There may be trouble ahead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,FThe logic of the Sky/ITV deal is that
OL,7,Fby combining Sky's paid platforms with
OL,8,Fthe much wider reach of ITV's free-to-
OL,9,Fair service, the enlarged group could
OL,10,Fattract more subscribers and arrest
OL,11,Fthe decline in advertising revenue.
OL,13,FThere are also significant savings to
OL,14,Fbe made by cutting duplicate roles and
OL,15,Fsharing technology when the businesses
OL,16,Fmerge. "Synergies" will likely mean
OL,17,Fsome jobs are lost.
OL,26,@xD@HOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,FBy joining forces, Sky and ITV will
OL,7,Fargue they stand a better chance of
OL,8,Fcompeting in a world dominated by much
OL,9,Flarger, better-resourced American
OL,10,Fstreamers, as well as platforms such
OL,11,Fas YouTube and TikTok.
OL,13,F"(The new business would) be a good-
OL,14,Fsized player in a world of giants,"
OL,15,Fone source said.
OL,17,FWhen the proposed tie-up was first
OL,18,Fannounced last November, Peer
OL,19,FBazalgette, a former Chairman of ITV,
OL,20,Fsaid he believed the consolidation of
OL,21,FBritish broadcasters was inevitable.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@BpmuD@YpnvD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,F"Think about our own viewing habits,"
OL,7,Fhe told ITV News.
OL,9,F"How often do we watch the public
OL,10,Fservice broadcasters? But they matter,
OL,11,Fthey deliver incredibly important
OL,12,Fpublic service news. We need that in
OL,13,Fthe mad world of the internet and the
OL,14,FAI world we are in now."
OL,16,FEven if a deal is agreed, significant
OL,17,Fhurdles remain.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@eO]qD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,FThe Competition and Markets Authority
OL,7,Fand Ofcom would both need to approve
OL,8,Fit, while the final decision would
OL,9,Frest with the Culture Secretary, Lisa
OL,10,FNandy.
OL,12,F"ITV and Sky's opening pitch is that
OL,13,Ftogether they account for around 10%
OL,14,Fof digital advertising spend, not 70%
OL,15,Fof TV advertising," someone close to
OL,16,Fthe negotiations said.
OL,18,F"It's hard to argue otherwise - Google
OL,19,Fand Meta is where the ad money has
OL,20,Fmoved; linear television is slowly
OL,21,Fdying."
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@SO]zD@AOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,FThey added: "Although there are bound
OL,7,Fto be objections from Channel 4 and
OL,8,FChannel 5."
OL,10,FSky's purchase of ITV's 40% stake in
OL,11,FITN is also potentially difficult -
OL,12,Fpartly because of the large and
OL,13,Fstubborn deficit in ITN's final salary
OL,14,Fpension scheme, a liability no one
OL,15,Fwants, but mainly because ITN produces
OL,16,Fnews for Channel 4 and Channel 5 as
OL,17,Fwell as ITV.
OL,26,@nD@MOUpD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30918
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,FExpect scrutiny and debate over
OL,7,Fwhether Comcast and Sky would end up
OL,8,Fwith too much influence over multiple
OL,9,Fnews providers in the UK.
OL,11,FSky is prepared to commit to honouring
OL,12,Fthe terms of ITV's Public Service
OL,13,FBroadcasting licence, which requires
OL,14,Fit to provide national and regional
OL,15,Fnews, current affairs, and a specific
OL,16,Fquota of UK-made programmes. These
OL,17,Fobligations run until the end of 2034.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
