FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30919
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHowever, Comcast is not currently
OL,12,Fplanning to make a funding commitment
OL,13,Fsimilar to the one it made to support
OL,14,FSky News when it bought Sky in 2018,
OL,15,Fwhich guaranteed its budget, indexed
OL,16,Fto inflation for 10 years.
OL,18,FIt proved to be an expensive promise,
OL,19,Fbut protected the service through
OL,20,Frounds of cuts and belt-tightening
OL,21,Felsewhere.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30920
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778782268
OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,FOne Ofcom insider suggested that
OL,7,Ffunding could become an issue. "This
OL,8,Fdeal should be an opportunity to
OL,9,Fsecure increased investment in news.
OL,10,FOfcom will want to see it not just
OL,11,Fmaintained, but strengthened - at both
OL,12,FSky and ITV."
OL,14,FThat may be difficult.
OL,16,FSky currently spends around #140
OL,17,Fmillion a year on Sky News, with ITV
OL,18,Fspending a similar amount on national
OL,19,Fand regional news.
