OL,3,CSky and ITV insiders tell ITV News
OL,4,Ctakeover deal is 'weeks away'
OL,6,F"Net of advertising income, Sky News
OL,7,Floses more than #100 million a year -
OL,8,Fthat's a vast sum of money," one
OL,9,Finsider said.
OL,11,F"Comcast wants to spend less on news,
OL,12,Fnot more. And the government can't
OL,13,Fpush too hard - who else is bidding
OL,14,Ffor ITV? From ITV's perspective, this
OL,15,Fdeal is a godsend. The world is too
OL,16,Funpredictable to offer any guarantees
OL,17,Fon spending."
